Description:
VIBRANT LIFESTYLE LIVING IN DOCKLANDS
Surpassing even the highest of expectations for luxury living, this exquisite tri-level terrace home embraces a cutting-edge design, complemented by a vibrant lifestyle, moments from Melbourne's CBD.
Accessed via a secure intercom entry, the home's stylish dimensions have been brilliantly designed to draw in natural light, with a glorious gallery foyer and low-maintenance courtyard complementing the three children's bedrooms each with built-in-robes and serviced by a family bathroom with toilet plus laundry.
The master suite is positioned for utmost privacy on the top floor, boasting built-in-robes, sparkling dual vanity ensuite, plus a private retreat and balcony with views overlooking the Bolte Bridge.
Promoting effortless open plan living, a gourmet stone kitchen and meals zone is sure to keep the avid chef happy, showcasing stainless steel Miele appliances, including dishwasher, microwave, and built-in coffee machine, soft-close drawers, glass splashbacks, walk-in-pantry plus a breakfast bench.
The adjacent living and dining zone are carpeted for added comfort and spills out onto a sundrenched balcony where summertime BBQ's can be enjoyed with friends.
Further benefitting from a powder room, high ceilings, ducted heating and cooling, security alarm, intercom, water tank plus a triple garage with internal access.
All this and in a fabulous location just a stones' throw from the Yarra River Esplanade, Docklands shops, restaurants and cafes, buses, trams and trains, Marvel Stadium, close to Crown Casino, South Melbourne Market, Melbourne's CBD and many of Melbourne's premier tourist destinations.
*PHOTO ID REQUIRED AT ALL INSPECTIONS.

Description:
World Class Architectural Design
This superb light-filled apartment is situated in the world class Banksia Tower constructed by MAB without compromise in the pursuit of excellence and luxury. Positioned between the edge of Victoria Harbour and NewQuay Central Park - the apartment features a sleek north-facing interior with a sweeping curved balcony overlooking Victoria Harbour and the City skyline, a generous living and dining room including a stone/Miele equipped kitchen, two double bedrooms, one+WIRs, fully-tiled ensuite, second bathroom and concealed laundry.
Banksia Tower short listed for a World Architecture Award
Panoramic views
Cutting edge interiors
Sleek prestige Miele & stone kitchen
Video intercom security
Ducted air conditioning
Secure basement parking
Storage cage
Exceptional owner occupier investment potential
Enjoy an ultra-convenient lifestyle
Amenities
The Banksia provides the Docklands finest amenities on level 18 with 360deg panoramic views of the City, Victoria Harbour and Port Phillip Bay and include with two lounges, community kitchen, gymnasium plus an entertainers deck with hot tubs and barbeque areas from which to soak up the surrounds and stunning views. Plus the NorthQuay Central Park for additional recreation or dog walking.
Location
Enjoy a walk-to lifestyle from the heart of NewQuay and the ever improving features of the Docklands precinct including The District which features Hoyts Cinemas, Street hawker food outlets plus the soon to be opened fresh food complex The Market which will have butchers, delis, bakeries, coffee roasters, Woolworths supermarket and Dan Murphys. Other attractions include the NewQuay Central Park at the doorstep, easy access to Ron Barassi Snr Park, the Capital City Trail, Marvel Stadium, leading Universities, trams and Southern Cross Station plus the Skybus to Melbourne Airport.
Please contact Serena Su on 0499 083 362 or Lynn Lum on 0474 044 293 to arrange an exclusive inspection.

Description:
EXQUISITE VIEWS AT VICTORIA POINT
Showcasing inner-city chic with impressively proportioned open plan living, this 17th floor 1 bedroom (plus study) apartment at VICTORIA POINT is sure to impress even the most discerning buyers. Moments from the heart of the Melbournes CBD, enjoy a relaxed harbourside lifestyle with waterfront restaurants, convenient supermarket shopping and free CBD trams all on your doorstep.
Full sized kitchen with island bench, stone counter tops and stainless steel appliances opens onto a huge open plan living space with plenty of room for dining, living and study. Full length windows/sliding doors captures a truly unique view back out over the water.
Double bedroom with full length mirrored robes and also sharing a waterfront view, it boasts brilliant natural light and practical storage solutions. Functional central bathroom with stone benches, walk in shower and euro laundry.
Take advantage of secure undercover parking plus a storage cage, a concealed laundry, ducted heating and cooling, roller blinds, on-site building manager and concierge, secure intercom entry, and exclusive access to the building's facilities including a fully equipped gym

Description:
3 Balconies, 2 Car Spaces, 1 Outstanding Living Experience
A complete triumph when it comes to utterly luxurious and stunningly spacious apartment living in the prestigious Yarras Edge residential complex, this amazing 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom residence has a 6th floor position as well as three separate balconies!
This impeccable property needs to be seen to be believed, with a considered floorplan allowing for both open and private living. Youll spend hours lazing about in the relaxed central lounge and dining spaces, with this vast area adjoined by a stone kitchen with breakfast bar and stainless steel appliances. This space also opens out to a balcony which takes in breathtaking views of the CBD and marina below.
The master bedroom is privately tucked away from the main living hub and comes with a dual vanity ensuite, BIRs, and a private balcony, while a 2nd bedroom also has its own outdoor retreat with its own balcony. The 3rd bedroom is situated near the deluxe central bathroom and handy powder room which also has a European laundry.In addition to these main features, this home also comes with ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom entry, 2 secure car spaces, and access to RekDek incl. gym, pool, spa, steam room, and sauna.
Yarras Edge is a premium destination for those looking to make the Docklands switch. Youre located close to the amazing South Wharf which has a variety of sensational bars and restaurants as well as easy access to DFO shopping. This area is also near Crown Entertainment Complex, Southbank Promenade, and just over the Webb Bridge to the terrific Victoria Harbour precinct.

Description:
Stylish and brand new with awe-inspiring east and north views
Get ready to embrace the deluxe modern interiors, exceptional building facilities, and spectacular 29th floor views that come with this brand new 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom apartment which sits in the popular Marina Tower complex in the heart of the NewQuay precinct.
From bright full windows which allow for wonderful natural light to memorable views and exquisite attention to detail in every room, this remarkable apartment has a wealth of things to love. The bright and open lounge and dining hub has incredible vistas to north and east as well as access out to the covered balcony where the harbour and CBD will be in full sight.
Home cooks will love using the practical stone kitchen which comes with stainless steel Miele appliances. The master bedroom has walk-through robes along with a lavish private ensuite, while the 2nd bedroom with BIRs and pristine bathroom complete the major highlights. You also get to enjoy a European laundry, split system heating and cooling, secure intercom, and secure car space.
Marina Tower residents have access to a lobby lounge, library, private business centre, meeting rooms, cinema, lounge and billiard room, kitchen and dining area, rooftop pool, gym, and expansive deck, while youre in close proximity to restaurants including Docklands Pizzeria, Steakhouse Grill 66, and Oscars Table just to name a few, The District Docklands, Marvel Stadium, Ron Barassi Snr Park, Moonee Ponds Creek Trail, and trams.
To arrange an inspection, please contact Vicky Leong on 0452 486 860 or Charles Finnigan on 0437 204 556.

Description:
Bespoke & Contemporary Docklands Apartment
Located in the South Tower of the exclusive Watergate residential complex, this 2-bedroom apartment boasts contemporary class with a tranquil leafy outlook.
Bathed in natural light and nestled nicely on the 2nd floor, this beautiful apartment is the perfect choice for city professionals, small families and anyone looking for a modern pad in Victoria Harbour!
Step onto the polished floorboards in the impressive open space of the lounge and dining zone, as well as the immaculate marble kitchen with ample storage and stainless steel appliances. Floor-to-ceiling windows create an abundance of natural light, and access to your very own large private balcony makes for perfect alfresco living.
Enjoy 2 spacious bedrooms with built-in wardrobes, study nook in the master, and the well-appointed bathroom with laundry facilities. Other features include a second balcony accessible from the master, and access to impressive resident facilities including a heated lap pool, sauna, grassed rooftop garden and gymnasium.
Positioned in the coveted Victoria Harbour precinct, this glorious inner-city abode is just a short stroll away from Marvel Stadium, Southern Cross Station, trams and restaurants. With close vicinity to the CBD, South Wharf, Harbour Town and Crown Entertainment Complex the incredible Docklands precinct offers the lifestyle of your dreams!
This spacious apartment is ideal for the first homeowner or the astute investor. Call Myles Johansson on 0490 041 342 to add this property to your portfolio and reap the rewards!

Next door is the 2nd bedroom with BIR, while just near the entry you get to enjoy the deluxe central bathroom.
The spacious and relaxed central living hub boasts space for both lounge and meals areas, and steps out to the balcony where Victoria Harbour is in full view. Other features include a sleek kitchen with breakfast bar and stainless steel appliances, concealed laundry, reverse cycle heating and cooling, additional heating, secure intercom, secure car space, and access to a pool, spa, golf practice net, and gym.
Walk to amazing nearby restaurants including Bhoj Restaurant, Fish Bar, Oscars Table, and Steakhouse Grill 66 just to name a few. Youre also close to IGA X-Press supermarket, The District Docklands with superb shops and eateries, Marvel Stadium, and trams.

Description:
Conder Elegance with Large Outdoor Terrace
This stylish two bedroom apartment, situated on the fourth level of the Conder complex in the heart of NewQuay, Docklands. Featuring a curved shape and predominant glass façade - where beautifully designed apartments draw inspiration from the waterside location, highlighted by superb vistas of the city skyline.
Loaded with stylish features
Generous living area opens to a balcony with panoramic views
Superb timber & prestige Euro equipped kitchen
Two zoned bedrooms
Sleek central bathroom plus European laundry
Ducted heating and cooling
Video intercom entry
Storage cage
Secure car space
Amenities
The comprehensive resort-style amenities available to the fortunate residents of The Conder complex. Features include access to an indoor swimming pool and sauna plus a fully-equipped gym, which sits alongside a lush landscaped rooftop garden and barbeque area overlooking Harbour Esplanade.
Location
Enjoy a walk-to lifestyle from the edge of NewQuay with the ever-improving features of the Docklands precinct. The popular District Docklands features Hoyts Cinemas, Street hawker food outlets plus the soon to be opened fresh food complex The Market which will have butchers, delis, bakeries, coffee roasters, Woolworths supermarket and Dan Murphys. Other attractions include easy access to the Bourke Street precinct including Docklands Park and Sports arena, Capital City Trail, Marvel Stadium, leading Universities, trams (free City Circle line), Southern Cross Station plus the Skybus to Melbourne Airport.

Description:
SPACIOUS AND BRIGHT
Whether you are a first home buyer or an astute investor, dont miss out on this incredible chance to buy in the Docklands. Located on La Trobe Street where Docklands meets the CBD sits the Lacrosse Building, ideally located next to Marvel Stadium, public transport, restaurants and shopping.
This light-filled apartment is a massive 88sqm internally, and has fantastic sweeping views from the CBD to the north of Melbourne. Enter in to the open plan living zone that includes a modern kitchen with stone bench tops and dishwasher, and floor to ceiling window presenting stunning views and providing plenty of light. Both bedrooms come with mirrored built in robes, with the master having a study nook and ensuite. The bathrooms come with clean, contemporary finishes, and a Euro-laundry in the main bathroom. A private balcony rounds out this well designed apartment.
Completing this chic Docklands apartment is split system heating & cooling, secure car space, and secure swipe &intercom entry, as well as use of the outdoor pool and gym.
Whether youre enjoying eating out with friends, swimming, shopping, or attending sporting events at Marvel Stadium, this is executive, low maintenance living without the price tag.
